Package ie.gmit.sw

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Documentor
    Documentor Interface describes a contract for all documentor objects.
    HashingStrategy
    HashingStrategy is an interface for all hashing methods (algorithms).
    Server
    Server is an interface that states what a server should do.
    Shingleator
    Shingleator Interface describes a contract for all shingling operators.
    SimilarityAlgorithm
    SimilarityAlgorithm Interface describes a contract for all similarity algorithms.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    Database class - The aim of this class was to provide a way of accessing the database for all the other classes.
    Document
    Document Object - Used as an abstract template of what each document should look like.
    DocumentorImpl
    Implementation of Documentor.
    HashCodeHashing
    HashCodeHashing is an implementation of HashingStrategy HashCode serves as a hashing function, this is the simple .hashCode() representation of shingles.The intention is to decouple classes and uphold the single responsibility rule.
    Hashing
    Hashing is a gateway method to be able to invoke an algorithm.
    JaccardAlgorithm
    JaccardAlgorithm is an implementation of Similarity Algorithm JaccardAlgorithm serves as a SimilarityAlgorithm, this is based on the Jaccard Index algorithm |A n B| / |A u B|.The intention is to decouple classes and uphold the single responsibility rule.
    MinHashHashing
    MinHashHashing is an implementation of HashingStrategy MinHash serves as a hashing function, this is the the act of creating a representation of shingles by getting the minimal hashcodes for each shingle and storing the first 200.The intention is to decouple classes and uphold the single responsibility rule.
    ProxyServer
    ProxyServer is an implementation of Server.
    ServerImpl
    ServerImpl is an implementation of Server.
    ServiceHandler  
    ServicePollHandler  
    ShingleatorImpl
    ShingleatorImpl is an implementation of Shingleator ShingleatorImpl serves as a simple shingle function that creates shingles of size n.
    SimilarityCalculator
    SimilarityCalculator is a gateway method to be able to invoke an algorithm.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HashingMethod
    Enum to specify which hashingMethod to use.
